# NOTE: public/app-assets (the Vite build output) IS committed so the production
# deploy ships a working compiled frontend via `git pull` (the on-server
# `vite build` is not reliably running, and the old public/build is owned by
# another user). Rebuild + commit public/app-assets when changing frontend code.
/public/hot
/public/storage
/public/images/testimonials/*
!/public/images/testimonials/.gitkeep
# Admin-uploaded videos live on the server; keep only the seeded testimonial clips in git.
/public/videos/*
!/public/videos/testimonial-1.mp4
!/public/videos/testimonial-2.mp4
!/public/videos/testimonial-3.mp4
/storage/*.key
/storage/pail
